Name: Cantaloper
About the game: Cantaloper is a very difficult platformer in which you use your legs to charge jumps and climb out of a deep pit. You'll play as a beautiful cantaloupe with human legs that must ascend out from the underground depths he finds himself in. There are no checkpoints; every fall will set you back based solely on how far you fall. Can you make it up two long levels? Will you elope? Featuring: - The sexiest cantaloupe you will ever see - A long journey to the surface - Rats - L I M B S Made in collaboration with IDislikeNames.
